<p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;"><span>The idea, put forth by Plato in </span><em>The Republic</em=
><span>, is that the ideal polis, the </span><em>kallipolis</em><span>, or =
beautiful city, should be ruled by philosophers who love knowledge, who see=
